    "label": "LandXML Export",
    "chart": "stateDiagram-v2\n  [*] --> activating\n\n  activating --> Running : canExecute\n  activating --> closing : else (inferred — DefaultExecuteTesterC never false)\n\n  state Running {\n    [*] --> MainPage\n\n    state MainPage {\n      note right of MainPage\n        Plain mode controls:\n          CTRL_MeasJob (job combo, read-only)\n          [CTRL_JobKind + typed job combo — v1.2/ExtTags only]\n          CTRL_OutputDevice / CTRL_FolderName / CTRL_FileName\n          GeoCloud upload checkbox\n          Send2Mail combo\n        Stylesheet mode adds (before output):\n          CTRL_StyleSheetProtected (checkbox — *.lss vs *.xsl)\n          CTRL_StyleSheetFile (file-browse combo)\n          CTRL_StyleSheetPassword (pwd, max 16 chars, hidden when unprotected)\n          CTRL_StyleSheetDescPrompt / CTRL_StyleSheetDesc (read-only, 90 chars)\n        FK5 shown/hidden by OnXslControlEvent → HasDynamicDialog(path)\n      end note\n    }\n\n    MainPage --> Verifying : F1\n    MainPage --> Settings : SHF1\n    MainPage --> XslParameters : F5 [isStylesheetMode AND HasDynamicDialog]\n    MainPage --> closing : ESC\n\n    Verifying --> MainPage : INPUT_INVALID / MSG_ACK / ESC\n    Verifying --> Exporting : INPUT_VALID / F1\n\n    Exporting --> ExportComplete : EXPORT_OK\n    Exporting --> ExportError : EXPORT_FAILED / XSL_WRONG_PASSWORD\n    Exporting --> MainPage : EXPORT_MORE / resetForMoreData\n    Exporting --> closing : EXPORT_CLOSE\n\n    state ExportComplete {\n      note right of ExportComplete\n        E_EXP_OK tail:\n          MessageShow(I_EXPORT_OF_DATA_COMPLETE_TOK)\n          ClearConfig; optional zip of images folder\n          If Send2Mail enabled → async send, then HandleSessionFinished\n          If GeoCloud enabled →\n            IsInternetAvailable? No → ShowNoInternetConnectionDialog\n                                Yes → StartUpload → OnUploadFinish\n          FinishExport:\n            ShowMessageBox(eMsgTypeConfirmation) Yes/No\n            Close(EC_KEY_QUIT)\n            Yes → ExecuteCommand(CMD_FUNC_SHOW_JOB_CONTEXT_MENU_EXPORT_DATA)\n      end note\n    }\n    ExportComplete --> MainPage : MSG_ACK / F1 / ENTER / ESC\n\n    state ExportError {\n      note right of ExportError\n        Error arms (MSG_Error, MBR_Ok):\n          NoDiskSpace             → M_CMN_EXP_NO_FREE_SPACE_TOK\n          OutputFileOpenError     → M_CMN_EXP_FILE_OPEN_ERROR_TOK\n          NoneCoordinateSystem    → M_CMN_EXP_RTK_NONE_COORD_SYSTEM_TOK\n          ApplyXslFailed_WrongPassword\n                                  → M_STYLESHEET_WRONG_PASSWORD_TOK\n                                    + remove output file\n          _ComFailed / _LoadXmlFailed /\n          _ConversionFailed / _LoadXslFailed\n                                  → M_DATA_CONVERSION_USING_STYLESHEET_FAILED_TOK\n                                    + remove output file\n          _VersionMismatch        → hardcoded version-mismatch string\n          default                 → \"Unexpected termination %d\"\n        ClearConfig() always called after switch\n      end note\n    }\n    ExportError --> MainPage : MSG_ACK / F1 / ENTER / ESC\n\n    state Settings {\n      note right of Settings\n        Plain mode — three tabs:\n          \"Export\" (LxmlConfigExportDlgC):\n            Points (read-only), Lines, Areas,\n            Images, ImageGroups,\n            TPS Measurements,\n            TPS Scan Information (enabled iff TPS Meas checked),\n            GPS Measurements, Point Codes, Free Codes,\n            Application Data, Coordinate Systems\n          \"LandXML\" (LxmlConfigLandXmlDlgC):\n            Dimensions combo (2D / 3D)\n            LandXML Version (1.0 / 1.1 / 1.2)\n            Use Extension Tags checkbox (v1.2+ only)\n            HeXML Schema Version (1.6…2.3, when ext tags enabled)\n            All disabled for Road/Rail/Tunnel/DTM job types\n          \"Geometry\" (LxmlConfigGeometryDlgC):\n            Export as Multi-Arc\n            Export Closed Lines as Parcels (default: on)\n        Stylesheet mode — Geometry tab only\n          (Export + LandXML tabs suppressed; FK2/Config disabled)\n      end note\n    }\n    Settings --> Settings : TAB_CHANGED / PAGE\n    Settings --> MainPage : F1 / CONFIG_DONE / CTRL_CLOSED / ESC\n\n    state XslParameters {\n      note right of XslParameters\n        XslConfigTabbedController (CID_XslParameters):\n          Build(): XslConfigFile::GetDialogDefinition extracts\n            \"DynamicDialog\" JSON from XSL comment block;\n            DynamicTabController::Build parses JSON → tabs + controls;\n            XslConfigFile::UpdateModel seeds values from xsl:param tags\n          FK1 = CONT (Close(EC_KEY_CONT))\n          SHFK5 = Default (DynamicTabController::OnSHF5Pressed →\n            DynamicDialogBuilder::LoadDefaults for active tab)\n          OnControllerClosed(EC_KEY_CONT) →\n            XslConfigFile::UpdateXsl writes param values back to .xsl\n          Control types: textbox, checkbox, string, integer, float,\n            combobox, date, time, ip, slider, angle, distance, area,\n            volume, pressure, temperature, grade, azimuth, lat/lon, …\n          Visibility: JSON \"Visible\" expressions support ==/!=/</>/AND/OR\n      end note\n    }\n    XslParameters --> XslParameters : TAB_CHANGED / PAGE\n    XslParameters --> MainPage : F1 / CONFIG_DONE / CTRL_CLOSED / ESC\n  }\n\n  Running --> closing : CLOSE\n\n  closing --> Running : CLOSE_VETOED (template shape — never fired)\n  closing --> garbageCollecting : CONFIRM_CLOSE\n  garbageCollecting --> Closed : APP_CLOSED\n  Closed --> [*]"
